Package io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.list

Interface ItemListService

All Superinterfaces:
Insertion
All Known Implementing Classes:
ItemListServiceImpl
public interface ItemListService extends Insertion
Provides an interface for interacting with item lists in a web context. This service offers methods to select, deselect, verify, and retrieve items, supporting both default and custom item list component types. By extending Insertion, it integrates seamlessly with broader test automation workflows.
